column17:
Product Description

CETUS ARGAN OIL SERIES evolves from one of the nature's well kept magic secrets so far- THE ARGAN OIL. Argan oil is extracted from kernels of the Argan Tree - the most ancient and rarest species of trees on Earth found only in Morocco. Argan oil remains one of the rarest oils in the world due to the small and very specific growing areas where the nearly extinct Argan trees are under the protection of UNESCO. The Argan oil is now accepted world wide as "Liquid Gold" due to its miraculous hair reviving and anti- aging properties. Immensely rich in carotenoids antioxidants sterols saponins squalene vitamin E and essential fatty acids in an easily absorbable formulation by skin and hair this unique blend of natural rare and essential components makes CETUS ARGAN OIL SERIES work wonders to revive your body from head to toe and turns back time! NATURAL HEALTHY AND MILD FORMULA which is free of sulfates phosphates mineral oil and parabens is suitable for all types of skin hair and scalp. Excellent repairability to restore damaged hair into healthy natural and silky finish without any residues.
